"SELECT " +" VALUE " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"WHERE " +" NAME = 'PAST_RESULT_ENTRY_TYP'"
"SELECT " +" PROC_EXEC_DATE " +"FROM " +" SYS_ACTUAL_COST_CTRL_AC " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\" " +"FROM " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" WH_CD = ?"
"select " +" COUNT(1) " +"from " +" T_INSPC_DEFECT " +"where " +" T_INSPC_DEFECT.PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" and T_INSPC_DEFECT.ACPT_NO = TO_NUMBER(?) " +" and ROWNUM <= NVL(TO_NUMBER(?), ROWNUM) + 1"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(EXCH_RATE) AS EXCH_RATE " +"FROM " +" T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" MAX(INSPC_ACPT_NO) AS INSPC_ACPT_NO, " +" MAX(CRCT_NO) AS CRCT_NO " +" FROM " +" T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT " +" WHERE " +" T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.ACPT_NO = to_number(?) " +" ) TPIA " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.ACPT_NO = to_number(?) " +" AND T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.INSPC_ACPT_NO = TPIA.INSPC_ACPT_NO " +" AND T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.CRCT_NO = TPIA.CRCT_NO " +" AND T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.CRCT_TYP = 2 " +" AND T_PAST_INSPC_ACPT.INSPC_ACPT_GNR_TYP = 2"
